snippet.textDisplay: No bill. You don't decide for me what is safe. Rediculous anyone has to die without loved ones there. My choice. We have been overreacting to this due to the fear mongering. Everywhere I go people are complying. So how is this doing anything? Small pockets of people causing this to persist? Really? Hospital employees wouldn't need to be the extended family. What happened to the flu, colds, pneumonia, herpes. Are we shutting down for the myriad of contagious crap out there? If you wish to wear a mask the rest of your life be my guest, but, this does not give you the right to push it on me.

snippet.textDisplay:
Its a Spiritual war that's going on.

Of course folks are dying

Are they dying for Christ or are they on their death bed afraid because they might not know where their going
 to end up.

Only God knows.

Ecclesiastes 3:2 KJV — A time to be born, and a time to die; a time to plant, and a time to pluck up that which is planted;


Philippians 1:21 KJV — For to me to live is Christ, and to die is gain.


Live for Christ folks not yourself.

Revelation 2:10 KJV — Fear none of those things which thou shalt suffer: behold, the devil shall cast some of you into prison, that ye may be tried; and ye shall have tribulation ten days: be thou faithful unto death, and I will give thee a crown of life.


We are to be faithful unto death not being afraid because these people lie to us.

This life isn't about self preservation.
25He that loveth his life shall lose it; and he that hateth his life in this world shall keep it unto life eternal.

26If any man serve me, let him follow me; and where I am, there shall also my servant be: if any man serve me, him will my Father honour.

John 12
